Our code was deploying but in the driver station it was showing No Robot Code so we installed Gradle 8.0

Gradle 8 hasn’t been released yet, which is why it can’t be downloaded. You should be using gradle 7.5.1.

What was in the riolog and deriver station messages window when your code deployed but the driver station showed no code?
